==============================
========== 02/09/18 ==========
==============================

I) Summary
	A) Created App Icons
	B) Set Default Colors
	C) Removed Sidebar
	D) Implemented Horizontal Nav
	E) Added R Logo to Toolbar

II) Log:

A) Created App Icons
	- Icon Generator:
	- Generated Icons and saved them in app > src > main > res
		- mipmap-*

B) Default Colors:
	- app > res > colors.xml
	- used shade picker for colorPrimary Dark #7d1b2a
		- http://www.color-hex.com/color/9d2235

C) Removed Sidebar
	- File -> new -> Activity -> Empty Activity -> Add to Launcher
	- Removed old activity from AnroidManifest.xml
	- Deleted layouts and homepage activity

D) Implemented Horizontal Nav
	- Used HorizontalScrollView Object & Buttons
	- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=issWruPBcWc
	`
    <HorizontalScrollView
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        app:layout_constraintTop_toBottomOf="@+id/toolbar_main">

        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content">

            <Button
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:text="News"/>
            ...
        </LinearLayout>
    </HorizontalScrollView>
    `

E) Added R logo to toolbar
	- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GsbYYY6wlx0
	- res > values > styles.xml
		- set style parent="Them.AppCompat.Light.NoActionBar"
	- New Toolbar in activity_main.xml
		- android:theme="@style/MyTheme"



